(274007, 9094, 273900, 'Asif Ali', 6105, '', 1339773171, '[QUOTE=Faisji;273900]NO,you can''t mix oil and water\n\nOn any gun (e.g cougar)as soon as hammer is lowered its on condition 3.All guns with a decocker are on condition 3 when decocked.\n.[/QUOTE]\nI would disagree with this. In condition 3, Chamber is empty. While decocker function is to lower the hammer after racking/loading the chamber i.e. chamber is loaded, in Decocker guns after decocking the gun can be said in Condition 2 (better representation will be Condition 1.5):)', 1, 0, '113.203.172.21', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
