(276942, 9172, 276887, '12GAUGE', 608, '', 1340912836, 'No need to panick bro. The chrome inside 8aikal''s barrel or any other barrel that is chrome lined is not decorative chrome. Its actually a thick layer of chrome which is sort of light grey in color instead of typical silvery/flashy chrome color.\r\n\r\nSo..., nothing to worry about. Just enjoy your gun even if it is scratched. Scratches on decorative chrome can cause it to chip off. \r\n\r\nOn hard chrome these scratches are harmless as long as they are not deep enough to reveal the metal underneath and as long as chrome is not chipping off due to them.\r\n\r\nEnjoy happy and safe shooting.\r\n\r\nRegards.', 1, 1, '141.0.8.43', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
